channel.title: Need Help with my server!
channel.description: Ok, so heres the problem. When I run my server it say's 'Starting fr33sc4p3 server on 0.0.0.0:43594'. Well by then you think it should work...but no. I have a router and I did port forwarding but it still say's 'Starting fr33sc4p3 server on 0.0.0.0:43594' and won't let people in. NOTE: Im using The perfect compiler.[br][size=1]Posted on: May 14, 2007, 02:52:22 PM[/size][hr]anyone know the prob?
